ination can be efficiently\ncomputed in an identical way, and a fast code computing the full primordial\nrecombination spectrum with this method will be made publicly available soon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Nov 2012 21:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-21"}
